But Spring Data JPA [can&#39;t use][2] `Sort` with native queries:

&gt; Spring Data JPA does not currently support dynamic sorting for native queries, because it would have to manipulate the actual query declared, which it cannot do reliably for native SQL.

However you can use [Pageable][3] and its implementation [PageRequest][4] instead:

